rows.label: qst701702_msg0001
rows.name:
Bloody Lobsters? Hey, hey, you're
not getting yourselves involved
in trouble again, are you?

rows.label: qst701702_msg0002
rows.name:
If you're asking if I know,
well, I've heard of them. Their
brutal methods are famous.

rows.label: qst701702_msg0003
rows.name:
I don't know why you're interested
in them, but don't get involved.
Nothing good will come of it.

rows.label: qst701702_msg0004
rows.name:
You know what they say, right?
"Only those prepared to be killed
should stick their necks out."
